casebody.data:
Lang et al. v. Hanlon (et al., Appellant). (No. 183,

March T., 1931.)

November 23, 1931:

Opinion by

Mr. Justice Maxey,

The judgment of the court below entering judgment n. o. v: for the defendant, M. A. Hanlon, is affirmed for the reasons set forth in the opinion filed to No. 182, March Term, 1931.
